dyMessageOne _other":"\u003cstrong id=\"1\"\u003e{{queued}} products\u003c/strong\u003e with enhanced titles and descriptions are queued to be visible to people on Pinterest in \u003cstrong id=\"2\"\u003e2–4 hours\u003c/strong\u003e, depending on how often your product catalogue feed refreshes.","A campaign with product groups cannot contain ad groups with mixed billable events when using campaign budget optimization --- m10n":"A campaign with product groups cannot contain ad groups with mixed billable events when using campaign budget optimization","Ad Groups within campaigns with product groups only accept excluded keywords. --- [m10n].createFlow.validationErrors.ONLY_EXCLUDE_ALLOWED_FOR_AD_GROUPS_IN_CATALOG_SALES":"Ad Groups within campaigns with product groups only accept excluded keywords.","Ad Groups within campaigns with product groups only accept excluded keywords. --- m10n":"Ad Groups within campaigns with product groups only accept excluded keywords.","Ad groups in campaigns with product groups using campaign budget must have the same optimization. --- [m10n] errorMessageRepo.bulkEditor.MIXED_SHOPPING_OPTIMIZATION_NOT_ALLOWED":"Ad groups in campaigns with product groups using campaign budget must have the same optimization.","Ad groups in campaigns with product groups using campaign budget must have the same optimization. --- [m10n]createFlow.validationErrors.mixedShoppingOptimizationNotAlowed":"Ad groups in campaigns with product groups using campaign budget must have the same optimization.","Archived products with enhanced titles and descriptions are moved to \u003cstrong id=\\\"1\\\"\u003eArchived\u003c/strong\u003e where they can be retrieved for later use. Archiving does not remove products from your catalog. --- Catalogs.Enhancements.ArchiveConfirmationModalManagedGa.bodyMessageTwo":"Archived products with enhanced titles and descriptions are moved to \u003cstrong id=\"1\"\u003eArchived\u003c/strong\u003e where they can be retrieved for later use. Ar